data.description: More photos to come.  Cozy wood sided cabin in  North Georgia  1/2 mile from the south corner of  Lake Burton. 2BR 2B. No restrictions. Good income producing rental history.Large deck that wraps around 3 sides and wood burning fireplace.New windows through out. Recent stainless still appliances and hard surface counter tops.vaulted ceilings, pine floors,  walls and ceiling gives this the mountain charm you are looking for. Small branch runs a long the border of lot. Close to award winning trout fishing, hiking ,ORV trails and US Forest Service. Centrally located between Helen, Clayton and Hiawassee
